{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 363, "height": 28, "text": "Step 01 핵심 개념 관계도", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 363.0, "height": 316, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 333, "height": 286, "text": "개발자 PC\nNode.js (런타임)\n패키지 매니저  package.json  node_modules\n(npm/pnpm/yarn)  (설계도)  (설치된 패키지)\nVite (빌드 도구)\n개발 서버 (Dev)  ESModule  HMR\n빌드 (Prod)  Rollup  번들/최적화\nVS Code (편집기)\nESLint (품질)\nPrettier (스타일)\n▼\n브라우저 (런타임)\n번들된 JS + CSS + 에셋 → React가 DOM 생성·업데이트", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}